T02D2438:49b-1: ta th'a t'a drishti n'a ma /
T02D2438:49b-3: de bzhin nyid kyi lta ba zhes bya ba /
T02D2438:49b-4: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2438:49b-5: de bzhin nyid kyi shing drung la //
T02D2438:49b-6: rtsa ba yal ga dmigs pa med //
T02D2438:49b-8: kye ma shing 'di ngo mtshar ltos //
T02D2438:49b-9: sa bon myu gu med pa yi //
T02D2438:49b-11: de yi rang bzhin ji lta bu //
T02D2438:49b-12: nam mkha' chang par bcug nas ni //
T02D2438:49b-13: khu tshur dag gis gcog pa bzhin //
T02D2438:49b-14: shing de gcog pa de dang 'dra //
T02D2438:49b-15: rtsa ba dag kyang yod 'gyur la //
T02D2438:49b-16: yal ga dag kyang yod pa yi //
T02D2438:49b-17: shing gis nam mkha' khyab par snang //
T02D2438:49b-18: kye ma ltos dang 'di dag la //
T02D2438:49b-19: nam mkha' khyab pa ngo mtshar che //
T02D2438:49b-20: kye ma shing 'di ngo mtshar ltos //
T02D2438:49b-21: sa bon myu gu med pa yi //
T02D2438:49b-23: de bzhin nyid kyi shing 'di yi //
T02D2438:49b-24: mtshan nyid khyod kyis rtogs pa med //
T02D2438:49b-25: bdag gis bstan par rtogs par 'gyur //
T02D2438:49b-26: dha ri pa ni smra bar byed //
T02D2438:49b-27: 'di la le lo byas pa yis //
T02D2438:49b-28: mtha' ru phyin par ma gyur bas //
T02D2438:49b-29: bar du phung bar ma byed cig / kye ma shing 'di ngo mtshar ltos //
T02D2438:49b-30: sa bon myu gu med pa yi //
